Dialogue: 0.0:00:04.57.0:00:08.65.Default..0.0.0..WHAT JUST HAPPENED?\NWHAT DID YOU JUST DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:08.67.0:00:10.05.Default..0.0.0..WHY ARE YOU DOING THAT\NWITH VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:10.07.0:00:11.32.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. THE DAMAGE IS DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:11.34.0:00:13.38.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD NEVER CHEAT ON HIM.\NYOU DID. THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:13.41.0:00:15.62.Default..0.0.0..MIKE CALLED THE UNIT\NTO CALL JIONNI
Dialogue: 0.0:00:15.64.0:00:17.56.Default..0.0.0..AND TELL HIM EVERYTHING\NTHAT FUCKING HAPPENED
Dialogue: 0.0:00:17.58.0:00:18.76.Default..0.0.0..WITH YOU AND MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:18.78.0:00:21.03.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU. MIKE!\NMIKE. I'M NOT KIDDING!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:21.05.0:00:22.76.Default..0.0.0..WHOA!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:22.79.0:00:24.66.Default..0.0.0..NO PHONE CALL WAS EVER MADE!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.69.0:00:27.73.Default..0.0.0..HE GOT PUNCHED IN THE FACE.\NHE RAN INTO A WALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:27.76.0:00:30.04.Default..0.0.0..AND NOW HE'S GETTING CHAMPAGNE\NBOTTLES THROWN AT HIS HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:30.06.0:00:33.74.Default..0.0.0..HOW MANY WAKE-UP CALLS\NDOES MIKE NEED?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:35.50.0:00:37.51.Default..0.0.0..DJ PAULY DELVECCHIO!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:37.53.0:00:39.84.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING\NTO JERSEY SHORE. BITCH!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:39.87.0:00:42.55.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\NWE GOT A SITUATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:42.57.0:00:44.45.Default..0.0.0..I'M THE SWEETEST BITCH\NYOU'LL EVER MEET.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:46.84.0:00:49.89.Default..0.0.0..AFTER I HAVE SEX WITH A GUY.\NI WILL RIP THEIR HEADS OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:49.91.0:00:52.19.Default..0.0.0..GO. VINNY! GO. VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:52.21.0:00:54.13.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU LIKE THE BOOBS?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.15.0:00:56.38.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:00:59.02.0:01:00.97.Default..0.0.0..CAN WE TALK ABOUT\NTHE OTHER NIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:00.99.0:01:03.13.Default..0.0.0..I THOUGHT WE WERE JUST.\NLIKE. CUDDLING AND...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:03.16.0:01:05.97.Default..0.0.0..MY PENIS WAS CUDDLING\NWITH YOUR VAGINA. BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:05.99.0:01:09.64.Default..0.0.0..I-I HAVE TO TELL HIM.\NTELL HIM. DON'T LIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:09.67.0:01:11.98.Default..0.0.0..GOD. SHIT BALLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:14.30.0:01:15.68.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:15.70.0:01:17.01.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA HATE ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:17.04.0:01:20.39.Default..0.0.0..REMEMBER WHAT I TOLD YOU.\NWHAT HAPPENED WITH VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:20.41.0:01:21.62.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:21.64.0:01:23.68.Default..0.0.0..WE HAD SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:28.95.0:01:32.43.Default..0.0.0..I GIVE YOU A SECOND CHANCE\NAND THIS IS WHAT...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:32.45.0:01:35.10.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS WHAT YOU TELL ME AFTER\NI GIVE YOU A SECOND CHANCE?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:35.12.0:01:38.37.Default..0.0.0..BABE. I HAD NO IDEA\NWHAT HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:38.39.0:01:39.87.Default..0.0.0..I JUST FOUND OUT TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:39.90.0:01:41.71.Default..0.0.0..I JUST TALKED TO VINNY.\NAND I WAS LIKE. "LISTEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:41.73.0:01:42.74.Default..0.0.0..WHAT HAPPENED?"
Dialogue: 0.0:01:42.76.0:01:44.58.Default..0.0.0..HE WAS LIKE. "LISTEN.\NYOU WERE DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.60.0:01:46.58.Default..0.0.0..YOU TOLD ME YOU WERE DONE.\NYOU WERE SINGLE."
Dialogue: 0.0:01:46.60.0:01:48.95.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS MY OWN FAULT\NBECAUSE I WAS SO MAD AT YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.97.0:01:50.65.Default..0.0.0..IT'S NOT EVER GONNA HAPPEN\NAGAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:50.67.0:01:51.88.Default..0.0.0..I PROMISE YOU.\NIT JUST...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:51.91.0:01:53.45.Default..0.0.0..WHAT WOULD YOU DO\NIF I DID THAT TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:53.48.0:01:54.85.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD KILL SOMEONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:54.88.0:01:58.36.Default..0.0.0..YOU... YOU RUINED ME WHEN I\NTHOUGHT YOU GUYS JUST HOOKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:58.38.0:02:00.16.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU THINK I'M GOING\NTHROUGH RIGHT NOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:00.18.0:02:02.66.Default..0.0.0..NO. I GET IT. I GET IT.\NI'M SORRY. I FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:02.69.0:02:04.96.Default..0.0.0..I'M A FUCKING LOSER.\NI'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:04.99.0:02:07.07.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. YOU DON'T BREAK UP\NWITH YOUR BOYFRIEND
Dialogue: 0.0:02:07.09.0:02:08.90.Default..0.0.0..AND FUCK SOMEONE\NAN HOUR LATER.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:08.92.0:02:10.27.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T DO THAT\NTO SOMEBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:10.29.0:02:12.24.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW\NWHAT ELSE TO SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:12.26.0:02:15.97.Default..0.0.0..MM. SO. LIKE.\NARE WE TOGETHER OR ARE WE...
Dialogue: 0.0:02:16.00.0:02:18.81.Default..0.0.0..LET ME KNOW.\NLIKE. JUST LET ME KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:23.17.0:02:25.62.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW. NICOLE.\NI DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:25.64.0:02:26.99.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO BE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:27.01.0:02:29.35.Default..0.0.0..BUT I JUST DON'T KNOW HOW\NI'M GONNA GET OVER THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:29.38.0:02:32.29.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW YOU DON'T LIKE THIS.\NBUT YOU NEED TO HANDLE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:32.31.0:02:34.49.Default..0.0.0..JUST BE WITH ME. PLEASE?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:34.52.0:02:36.63.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT'S GOING\NTHROUGH MY HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:36.65.0:02:38.66.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S GOING THROUGH MY STOMACH.\NMY BODY RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:38.69.0:02:40.00.Default..0.0.0..THINKING ABOUT\NWHAT YOU DID TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:40.02.0:02:42.17.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL SO BAD.\NLISTEN...
Dialogue: 0.0:02:42.19.0:02:43.74.Default..0.0.0..I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:43.76.0:02:46.30.Default..0.0.0..I CANNOT... CANNOT.\NRIGHT THIS SECOND.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:46.33.0:02:47.74.Default..0.0.0..CALL YOU MY GIRLFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.76.0:02:49.54.Default..0.0.0..BUT WHAT AM I?\NI'M NOT YOUR GIRLFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:49.57.0:02:52.88.Default..0.0.0..SO. I JUST DON'T WANT YOU\NTO FIND SOMEBODY ELSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.90.0:02:54.31.Default..0.0.0..WHAT YOU DID WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:54.34.0:02:57.58.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW HOW WE'RE GONNA\NEVER GET THROUGH THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:57.61.0:03:01.65.Default..0.0.0..OKAY. I GOTTA GO. OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:06.32.0:03:08.36.Default..0.0.0..HOW'D HE TAKE IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:08.38.0:03:09.79.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE WORKING ON THINGS.\NI GUESS.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:09.82.0:03:13.40.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT HIS GIRLFRIEND.\NBUT WE'RE WORKING ON THINGS.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.42.0:03:17.02.Default..0.0.0..WANT TO CUDDLE?\NVINNY! YOU DOUCHE!
Dialogue: 0.0:03:24.13.0:03:29.01.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:03:29.04.0:03:33.08.Default..0.0.0..DEE. DO YOU HAVE MEDICINE?\NI NEED SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:33.11.0:03:35.09.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL LIKE A BUTTHOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:38.05.0:03:42.29.Default..0.0.0..CAN YOU HUG ME?\NHUG YOU? YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.32.0:03:44.43.Default..0.0.0..CUDDLE? I'LL CUDDLE.\NI MEAN. I'M FREE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:44.45.0:03:45.90.Default..0.0.0..STOP BEING A CREEP.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.92.0:03:48.30.Default..0.0.0..VINNY. CAN YOU TELL PAULY TO\NHAVE SEX WITH MY FRIEND. PLEASE?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:48.32.0:03:49.33.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:49.36.0:03:50.84.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. SHE WANTS TO\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.86.0:03:52.00.Default..0.0.0..FOR REAL?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:52.03.0:03:53.44.Default..0.0.0..HOLY SHIT.\NDO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.46.0:03:54.81.Default..0.0.0..AT THIS POINT.\NI'M LIKE. FUCK IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:54.83.0:03:58.01.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I'M LEAVING SOON. SO ME\NAND PAULY SHOULD DO SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:58.03.0:03:59.41.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. YOU DON'T\NWANT TO DO SEX?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:59.43.0:04:02.11.Default..0.0.0..IT'S GONNA CAUSE OUR\NFRIENDSHIP TO GO MESSED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:02.14.0:04:03.65.Default..0.0.0..NO. IF WE DON'T LET IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:03.67.0:04:06.05.Default..0.0.0..WHAT IF HE'S BANGING YOU AND\NHIS NOSE STARTS BLEEDING ON YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:06.07.0:04:07.32.Default..0.0.0..IS YOUR NOSE BLEEDING?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.34.0:04:08.75.Default..0.0.0..IT'S ALL RIGHT\NBECAUSE IT'S PAULY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:08.78.0:04:10.72.Default..0.0.0..SHE'LL LIKE TO LICK IT.\NRIGHT? AHH.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.75.0:04:13.49.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE WHEN DEENA\NIS HITTING ON PAULY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:13.52.0:04:17.40.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE PAULY'S SUCH A NICE GUY\NAND HE CAN'T BE MEAN TO HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.42.0:04:18.96.Default..0.0.0..WHERE ARE YOU GUYS GOING\NTONIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:18.99.0:04:21.00.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NI THINK SHE'S DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:21.02.0:04:24.60.Default..0.0.0..JENNI'S SICK. SO I MIGHT WIND UP\NROLLING WITH YOU GUYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:24.63.0:04:26.34.Default..0.0.0..I THINK WE'RE GOING\NTO TWICE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:26.36.0:04:28.44.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN AFTER.\NME AND YOU COULD JUST DO SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.46.0:04:30.11.Default..0.0.0..FOR REAL?\NMM-HMM.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:30.13.0:04:32.31.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT'S UP.\NWHOO-HOO!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:32.33.0:04:34.55.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S GONNA GO ON TONIGHT.\NI GOTTA BRING HOME A GIRL
Dialogue: 0.0:04:34.57.0:04:36.78.Default..0.0.0..SO DEENA DOES NOT\NCOME INTO MY BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:36.81.0:04:38.18.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT TRYING TO SMUSH DEENA.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:38.21.0:04:39.92.Default..0.0.0..IT'S HAPPENING TONIGHT.\NYEAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:39.94.0:04:42.05.Default..0.0.0..BUT I WANT TO GO HARDER THAN\NYOU DID WITH THAT ONE GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:42.08.0:04:43.29.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?\NOH!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.31.0:04:44.76.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NWE'LL BREAK THE FUCKING BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:44.78.0:04:47.16.Default..0.0.0..HOLY SHIT.\NYEAH. SO...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:47.18.0:04:49.86.Default..0.0.0..I'M HORNY NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.89.0:04:52.10.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T GO ANYWHERE..
Dialogue: 0.0:04:52.12.0:04:53.53.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GOING OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:53.56.0:04:56.50.Default..0.0.0..LOOK AT ME.\NI'M JUST AS BAD AS YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:56.53.0:04:57.97.Default..0.0.0..♪ GONNA HAVE A GOOD TIME ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:04:57.99.0:05:00.64.Default..0.0.0..I'M RUNNING OUT OF GAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:00.66.0:05:02.11.Default..0.0.0..♪ GONNA HAVE A GOOD TIME ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.13.0:05:03.58.Default..0.0.0..CAB'S HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.60.0:05:04.58.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GO.\NROCK OUT. SON.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:04.60.0:05:07.14.Default..0.0.0..♪ WHOA. WHOA. WHOA ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:05:07.17.0:05:09.71.Default..0.0.0..♪ WHOA. WHOA.\NWHOA. WHOA ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:05:09.74.0:05:12.32.Default..0.0.0..JERSEY! JERSEY! JERSEY!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:12.34.0:05:14.05.Default..0.0.0..JERSEY!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.08.0:05:24.50.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.52.0:05:25.80.Default..0.0.0..YO. I NEED TO GET A GIRL
Dialogue: 0.0:05:25.82.0:05:27.60.Default..0.0.0..SO DEENA DOESN'T FUCK ME\NTONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:27.62.0:05:31.40.Default..0.0.0..TONIGHT IT IS A MUST THAT\NPAULY BRINGS HOME A CHICK
Dialogue: 0.0:05:31.43.0:05:35.34.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE DEENA HAS BEEN SAYING\NSHE WANTS TO BANG PAULY ALL DAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:35.36.0:05:37.34.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.37.0:05:41.15.Default..0.0.0..NICE TO MEET YOU.\NI'M REALLY SHY.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:41.17.0:05:42.91.Default..0.0.0..I GOT A DILDO TODAY!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:42.94.0:05:45.52.Default..0.0.0..YIKES.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.54.0:05:47.32.Default..0.0.0..YO. LET'S KEEP MOVING.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:47.34.0:05:54.53.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.55.0:05:56.79.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO\NTOUCH A GUY'S HAIR.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:56.82.0:06:00.20.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHAT?\NFUCK THAT SHIT!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:00.22.0:06:03.27.Default..0.0.0..I CAN TOUCH WHATEVER\NTHE FUCK I WANT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:03.29.0:06:04.87.Default..0.0.0..THIS GIRL'S NOT TOUCHING\NTHIS BLOW-OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.89.0:06:07.54.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. I'M LEAVING.\NDEENA'S STAYING.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:07.56.0:06:09.44.Default..0.0.0..MAKE SURE SHE COMES HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:09.46.0:06:10.84.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANT YOU\NTO FUCK HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:10.87.0:06:12.88.Default..0.0.0..OH. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.90.0:06:19.82.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:06:19.84.0:06:21.92.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S YOUR NAME?\NNICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:21.94.0:06:23.45.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU WANT TO COME WITH US?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:23.48.0:06:26.09.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO. BUT I HAVE TO\NTAKE MY FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:26.11.0:06:27.39.Default..0.0.0..I UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:27.42.0:06:28.73.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:06:28.75.0:06:30.66.Default..0.0.0..I STRUCK OUT TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:30.69.0:06:32.10.Default..0.0.0..I SEE THE CONDITION\NTHAT DEENA'S IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:32.12.0:06:34.07.Default..0.0.0..I MYSELF AM IN TROUBLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:34.09.0:06:35.67.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. DO YOU WANT TO\NHAVE SEX?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:35.69.0:06:37.70.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NI CAN'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:37.73.0:06:39.00.Default..0.0.0..HE'S ON HIS PERIOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:39.03.0:06:41.01.Default..0.0.0..THEN YOU'LL BREAK UP WITH ME\NFROM FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:41.03.0:06:43.77.Default..0.0.0..NO.\NYES. YOU WILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:43.80.0:06:45.68.Default..0.0.0..NO. I WON'T.\NDEENA'S HORNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:45.70.0:06:48.85.Default..0.0.0..PAULY IS DEFINITELY PART OF THE\NI-DOUBLE-F RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:48.87.0:06:50.75.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA HAVE\NALL KINDS OF CRAZY FEELINGS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:50.77.0:06:52.05.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW HOW GIRLS GET.\NNO!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:52.07.0:06:53.18.Default..0.0.0..YES. SIR.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:53.21.0:06:54.72.Default..0.0.0..ASK VINNY.\NI FUCK HIM IN THE ASS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:54.74.0:06:56.96.Default..0.0.0..HE FUCKS ME IN THE ASS.\NAND IT'S NEVER BEEN THE SAME.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:56.98.0:06:58.46.Default..0.0.0..NEVER BEEN THE SAME.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:58.48.0:07:00.29.Default..0.0.0..WELL. THE REAL REASON PAULY\NWON'T FUCK DEENA
Dialogue: 0.0:07:00.32.0:07:02.56.Default..0.0.0..IS BECAUSE PAULY\NDOESN'T LIKE MEATBALLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:02.58.0:07:04.00.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:04.02.0:07:05.70.Default..0.0.0..GO TELL HIM\NWHAT TO DO. VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:05.72.0:07:06.90.Default..0.0.0..VINNY. WHAT'S GOING ON?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:06.92.0:07:07.97.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANT TO\NFUCK DEENA TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:07.99.0:07:09.13.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE IT'S GONNA END OUR...
Dialogue: 0.0:07:09.16.0:07:10.50.Default..0.0.0..SHE WANTS TO {...} YOU?\NASK HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:10.53.0:07:13.50.Default..0.0.0..OH. HERE WE GO.\NHERE WE FUCKING GO RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:13.53.0:07:16.51.Default..0.0.0..IT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.\NSHUT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:16.53.0:07:18.44.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T WAIT TO GO HOME.\NTHEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:18.47.0:07:20.94.Default..0.0.0..VINNY AND NICOLE HAVE DONE SEX\NAND THEY'RE STILL COOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:20.97.0:07:23.11.Default..0.0.0..SO WHY CAN'T ME AND PAULY\NDO SEX AND BE COOL?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:23.14.0:07:25.92.Default..0.0.0..I THINK I'M PRETTY.\NYOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:25.94.0:07:27.95.Default..0.0.0..SO NOW I GOTTA DEAL\NWITH THIS. AND I'M GONNA RUIN
Dialogue: 0.0:07:27.98.0:07:29.12.Default..0.0.0..OUR FRIENDSHIP\N'CAUSE I'M NOT GONNA FUCK HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:29.14.0:07:30.52.Default..0.0.0..IF I FUCK HER.\NRUIN OUR FRIENDSHIP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:30.55.0:07:31.66.Default..0.0.0..IF I DON'T FUCK HER.\NI RUIN THE FRIENDSHIP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:31.68.0:07:33.22.Default..0.0.0..DON'T DO IT.\NWELCOME TO MY WORLD.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:33.25.0:07:34.76.Default..0.0.0..DAMNED IF YOU DO.\NDAMNED IF YOU DON'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:34.78.0:07:36.73.Default..0.0.0..NO. DAMNED IF YOU DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:36.75.0:07:41.03.Default..0.0.0..LISTEN. I AM A GOOD FUCK.\NDEENA!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:41.06.0:07:42.83.Default..0.0.0..OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:42.86.0:07:46.87.Default..0.0.0..AND I HAVE NO SHAME.\NNO. NO. DEENA.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:46.90.0:07:49.41.Default..0.0.0..I ONLY DO SEX WITH THE GUYS\NTHAT I ACTUALLY CARE ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:49.43.0:07:51.84.Default..0.0.0..AND I CARE ABOUT PAULY.\NSO I'D FUCKING FUCK HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:51.87.0:07:54.05.Default..0.0.0..DEENA. I WOULD KNOCK\NTHE DUST OFF THAT PUSSY
Dialogue: 0.0:07:54.07.0:07:55.28.Default..0.0.0..IF WE WEREN'T FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:55.30.0:07:57.38.Default..0.0.0..JUST SAYING.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:57.41.0:07:59.78.Default..0.0.0..HE'S BEEN TELLING ME\NALL NIGHT
Dialogue: 0.0:07:59.81.0:08:02.42.Default..0.0.0..THAT HE WANTS DEENA\NTO CLIMB INTO HIS BED
Dialogue: 0.0:08:02.44.0:08:06.42.Default..0.0.0..AND MERHP. MERHP.\NMERHP. MERHP.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:06.45.0:08:08.86.Default..0.0.0..AND HE'S LIKE. "OH. YEAH!\NOH. YEAH!"
Dialogue: 0.0:08:08.88.0:08:12.23.Default..0.0.0..WAKE UP. "YEAH! OH. YEAH!\NFUCKING DEENA. YEAH!"
Dialogue: 0.0:08:12.25.0:08:13.66.Default..0.0.0..DEE. YOUR TIT'S\NABOUT TO FALL OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:13.69.0:08:17.10.Default..0.0.0..NO. IT'S NOT. ASSHOLE.\NI FUCKING HATE THIS PLACE.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.13.0:08:20.64.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S PISS DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:20.66.0:08:23.24.Default..0.0.0..SHE WON'T EVEN REMEMBER\NWHAT HAPPENED TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:23.27.0:08:27.21.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL BAD. THOUGH.\NI SHOULD HAVE FUCKED HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:27.24.0:08:29.18.Default..0.0.0..TOUGH GUY!\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:29.20.0:08:30.51.Default..0.0.0..MIKE'S ACTING\NLIKE A TOUGH GUY.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:30.54.0:08:32.58.Default..0.0.0..BUT THIS TIME. YOU'RE GONNA\NGET EVERYBODY INVOLVED.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:32.61.0:08:34.05.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCK EVERY ONE\NOF THESE KIDS UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:34.08.0:08:35.89.Default..0.0.0..I'M READY TO GO RIGHT NOW.\NI DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:35.91.0:08:39.02.Default..0.0.0..WHOEVER MIKE'S BEEN FUCKING\NWITH HAS TO TELL HIM. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:39.05.0:08:41.66.Default..0.0.0.."YO. WE CAN'T DO THIS\NANYMORE."
Dialogue: 0.0:08:41.68.0:08:44.88.Default..0.0.0..IT'S EITHER LEAVE\NOR CHANGE. YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:50.83.0:08:52.30.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU SICK AT ALL?\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:52.33.0:08:54.84.Default..0.0.0..NO. I HAD. LIKE.\NA BREAKDOWN LAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:54.86.0:08:56.61.Default..0.0.0..OH. YOU DID?\NARE YOU OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:56.63.0:09:00.65.Default..0.0.0..I MISS PENIS.\NAND THE GUYS HERE SUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:00.67.0:09:03.31.Default..0.0.0..DEENA WAS LIKE.\N"I'M A FUCKING GOOD FUCK."
Dialogue: 0.0:09:03.34.0:09:05.95.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NNO. LIKE. I'M NOT EVEN...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:05.97.0:09:07.65.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS LIKE... AND PAULY\NWAS ACTUALLY. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:07.68.0:09:09.29.Default..0.0.0.."I DON'T WANT TO RUIN\NOUR FRIENDSHIP."
Dialogue: 0.0:09:09.31.0:09:10.76.Default..0.0.0..HE WAS LIKE.\N"IF WE WEREN'T FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.78.0:09:12.06.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD FUCK\NTHE SHIT OUT OF YOU."
Dialogue: 0.0:09:12.08.0:09:13.66.Default..0.0.0..HE SAID THAT?\NOR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:13.68.0:09:16.63.Default..0.0.0..DEENA!\NI MISS PENIS. I'M TELLING YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.65.0:09:18.83.Default..0.0.0..SHE HAD THE VAGINA\NFOR A WHILE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.85.0:09:20.03.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:20.05.0:09:22.30.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S LIKE. "YEAH."\NWHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:25.33.0:09:27.91.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.93.0:09:30.81.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. GIVE ME.\NLIKE. TEN MINUTES.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:30.83.0:09:33.58.Default..0.0.0..TODAY. I'M JUST FREAKING OUT\NABOUT JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:33.60.0:09:36.18.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I'VE NEVER FELT THIS WAY\NABOUT A GUY EVER IN MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:36.20.0:09:38.48.Default..0.0.0..SO I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHAT\NTHE FUCK TO DO RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:38.51.0:09:40.75.Default..0.0.0..ALL I WANT TO DO IS DRINK\NWITH MY MEATBALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:40.78.0:09:44.42.Default..0.0.0..OH. THE COWBOY HAT'S OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:44.45.0:09:48.06.Default..0.0.0..WHEN DEENA HAS THE COWBOY HAT\NON. THAT MEANS BUSINESS.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:48.08.0:09:50.60.Default..0.0.0..TEAM MEATBALLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:50.62.0:09:54.67.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.69.0:09:56.50.Default..0.0.0..WE LOOK SO CUTE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.53.0:09:58.67.Default..0.0.0..WE BELONG IN JERSEY\NWITH THESE OUTFITS.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:00.63.0:10:03.61.Default..0.0.0..WHOA. THAT'S A START.\NTHAT IS A START.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.63.0:10:05.14.Default..0.0.0..CIAO.\NCIAO.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:05.17.0:10:07.21.Default..0.0.0..WE WANT MUSIC!\NMUSIC!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.24.0:10:08.48.Default..0.0.0..MUSIC IN HERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:08.50.0:10:09.65.Default..0.0.0..THIS WAY.\NYOU READY TO SHAKE IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.67.0:10:10.65.Default..0.0.0..IS THE DJ HERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:10.67.0:10:13.35.Default..0.0.0..YEAH!\NYEAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.38.0:10:15.99.Default..0.0.0..WHOO-HOO!\NWE NEED MUSIC!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:16.01.0:10:18.89.Default..0.0.0..YO. WHERE'S THE DJ AT?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:18.91.0:10:20.69.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.72.0:10:23.13.Default..0.0.0..♪ LET'S BRING THE WALLS DOWN ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:23.15.0:10:25.23.Default..0.0.0..THE MEATBALLS\NCAN THROW A PARTY
Dialogue: 0.0:10:25.25.0:10:28.33.Default..0.0.0..AT ANY BORING RESTAURANT.\NEVEN IF IT'S 11:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:28.36.0:10:29.93.Default..0.0.0..♪ I FEEL THE CHANGE\NIN MYSELF ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:29.96.0:10:31.90.Default..0.0.0..♪ IT'S IN MY VEINS.\NIT'S IN MY HEALTH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.93.0:10:34.14.Default..0.0.0..♪ IT'S IN MY BRAIN.\NIT'S ON THE SHELF ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:34.16.0:10:35.54.Default..0.0.0..♪ TO GO INSANE\NACHIEVING WEALTH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:35.56.0:10:37.07.Default..0.0.0..♪ IT'S ALL THE SAME ♪\NAAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:37.10.0:10:38.64.Default..0.0.0..♪ IT'S ALL THE SAME.\NLET'S MAKE IT RAIN ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:10:38.67.0:10:40.04.Default..0.0.0..USUALLY WHEN\NNORMAL PEOPLE FALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.07.0:10:41.38.Default..0.0.0..THEY GET REALLY EMBARRASSED.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:41.40.0:10:42.95.Default..0.0.0..ME. I JUST GET UP.\NCOVER UP MY CUCA.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:42.97.0:10:44.18.Default..0.0.0..AND I JUST START DANCING\NAGAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:44.21.0:10:45.52.Default..0.0.0..PARTY DOESN'T STOP.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.54.0:10:47.99.Default..0.0.0..SHE CAN DO THE JERSEY TURNPIKE\NON ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:48.01.0:10:49.62.Default..0.0.0..THEY'RE ALLOWING IT.\NSO YOU CAN DO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:49.65.0:10:51.99.Default..0.0.0..CAN YOU TOUCH YOUR TOES?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:52.01.0:10:53.22.Default..0.0.0..CAN YOU SHAKE YOUR BUTT?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:53.25.0:10:55.66.Default..0.0.0..OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:55.68.0:10:57.13.Default..0.0.0..DO IT ON ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.15.0:11:00.53.Default..0.0.0..SORRY. MOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.56.0:11:02.70.Default..0.0.0..TEAM MEATBALLS!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:07.83.0:11:11.31.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}PERFECTO.\NPERFECTO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.33.0:11:13.48.Default..0.0.0..THE BATHROOM RIGHT NOW\NIS DISGUSTING.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.50.0:11:17.62.Default..0.0.0..AND THERE'S LIKE A DISGUSTING\NTOOTHBRUSH ON THE COUNTER.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:17.64.0:11:20.15.Default..0.0.0..NOW I'M GETTING ALL THE NASTY\NHAIR OUT OF THE CLIPPERS.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.18.0:11:21.92.Default..0.0.0..I JUST CLEANED THE SHIT\NOUT OF BOTH CLIPPERS.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:21.94.0:11:23.35.Default..0.0.0..I USED SOMEBODY'S TOOTHBRUSH.\NTOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:23.38.0:11:24.49.Default..0.0.0..ANYBODY DUMB ENOUGH TO LEAVE\NTHEIR TOOTHBRUSH
Dialogue: 0.0:11:24.51.0:11:25.79.Default..0.0.0..ON A COUNTER\NTHAT'S THIS DIRTY...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:25.81.0:11:26.98.Default..0.0.0..DESERVES IT.\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:28.92.0:11:32.33.Default..0.0.0..YO. CUT MY HAIR. BRO.\NCUT MY HAIR. DAWG.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:32.35.0:11:34.40.Default..0.0.0..MUHAMMAD ALI\NKNOCKED OUT JOE LOUIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:34.42.0:11:36.60.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}SI.{\i0}\NHIT ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:36.62.0:11:38.04.Default..0.0.0..HIT ME. MOTHERFUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:39.43.0:11:42.01.Default..0.0.0..TWO SECONDS LATER. MIKE\NCOMES IN. GRABS THE TOOTHBRUSH.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.03.0:11:45.84.Default..0.0.0..AND APPARENTLY IT'S HIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:49.77.0:11:51.75.Default..0.0.0..ON ONE SIDE OF ME.\NI FEEL A LITTLE BAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:51.77.0:11:53.68.Default..0.0.0..BUT ON THE OTHER SIDE OF ME.\NI'M LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.71.0:11:56.95.Default..0.0.0.."YES. YES. THIS IS AWESOME."
Dialogue: 0.0:11:56.98.0:12:00.16.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU WANT ME TO CUT YOU?\NYEAH. BUT I NEED A TOWEL.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:00.18.0:12:02.25.Default..0.0.0..I'M SWEATING.\NWHERE IS IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:04.99.0:12:07.06.Default..0.0.0..MIKE DIDN'T EVEN NOTICE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:07.09.0:12:09.70.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.72.0:12:13.40.Default..0.0.0..I COULD NOT FUCKING BELIEVE\NHE PICKED UP THAT TOOTHBRUSH.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:13.43.0:12:15.90.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS CRAZY. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:18.13.0:12:20.64.Default..0.0.0..CAN YOU JUST WALK\NAND I'LL FOLLOW YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:20.67.0:12:22.25.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT EVEN LOOKING.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:22.27.0:12:25.95.Default..0.0.0..DEENA. WAIT. DEENA. WAIT.\NDEENA. WAIT. DEENA!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:25.97.0:12:28.49.Default..0.0.0..TEAM MEATBALLS IS JUST LIKE.\NGO HARD OR GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:28.51.0:12:29.72.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WE DON'T CARE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:29.75.0:12:31.19.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WE'RE NOT GONNA GO\NHALF-ASSED.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:31.21.0:12:32.76.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. IF WE'RE DRINKING\NDURING THE DAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:32.78.0:12:34.19.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE FUCKING DRINKING\NALL NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:34.22.0:12:35.53.Default..0.0.0..WHO NEEDS TO BE\NAT WORK RIGHT NOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:35.55.0:12:37.86.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NIT IS SO COMFORTABLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:37.89.0:12:38.86.Default..0.0.0..♪ FANTASTIC ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:12:38.89.0:12:40.43.Default..0.0.0..♪ UH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:12:40.46.0:12:41.90.Default..0.0.0..♪ YEAH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:12:41.92.0:12:43.97.Default..0.0.0..♪ ALLOW ME\NTO INTRODUCE YOU ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:12:43.99.0:12:46.80.Default..0.0.0..♪ TO THE GREATEST WHITE PEOPLE\NIN THE WORLD ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:12:46.83.0:12:48.57.Default..0.0.0..YO. I'M ABOUT TO USE\NONE OF YOUR UNDERWEARS.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:48.60.0:12:49.84.Default..0.0.0..TAKE ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:49.86.0:12:51.94.Default..0.0.0..I AM. BECAUSE I'M RUNNING OUT\NOF UNDERWEAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:51.97.0:12:54.85.Default..0.0.0..TELL ME YOU BUSTED OUT\NTHE COMMUNION SHOES. BRO!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:56.04.0:12:58.68.Default..0.0.0..TONIGHT IS OUR LAST SATURDAY\NNIGHT IN ITALY.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:58.71.0:13:00.48.Default..0.0.0..WE DEFINITELY WANT TO GET\NA LITTLE DECKED OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.51.0:13:02.72.Default..0.0.0..RICO SUAVE.\NI LIKE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.74.0:13:04.96.Default..0.0.0..WHATEVER. HATER.\NI CAN'T EVEN LOOK AT RON.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.98.0:13:07.99.Default..0.0.0..LOOK. NO HIGH HEELS TONIGHT.\NI'M GOING MANDY. HOARD!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:08.02.0:13:09.29.Default..0.0.0..OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:09.32.0:13:11.09.Default..0.0.0..YO. WHEN YOU'RE TRYING TO\NDANCE ON THE TABLE
Dialogue: 0.0:13:11.12.0:13:13.10.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU HIT YOUR HEAD\NON A CHANDELIER.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:13.12.0:13:15.07.Default..0.0.0..GUIDETTE PROBLEMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.09.0:13:18.50.Default..0.0.0..GUIDO PROBLEMS ARE PROBLEMS\NTHAT. LIKE. GUIDOS RUN INTO.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:18.53.0:13:20.71.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE NO NAILS ON.\NWEAR SOMETHING ELSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:20.73.0:13:21.97.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE ALL FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:22.00.0:13:24.21.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. YOU LOOK SO CUTE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:24.23.0:13:27.71.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE LOSING OUR TANS.\NWE AIN'T BEEN TO THE GYM.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:27.74.0:13:29.45.Default..0.0.0..GUIDO AND GUIDETTE PROBLEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:29.47.0:13:32.55.Default..0.0.0..♪ I GOT MY SUIT ON\NTIGHT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:32.57.0:13:35.02.Default..0.0.0..♪ I GOT MY SHOES ON TIGHT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:35.04.0:13:36.19.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'M FANTASTIC ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:36.21.0:13:38.12.Default..0.0.0..♪ MY MANSION IS\NIT'S OUTSTANDING ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:38.15.0:13:41.06.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'M ON THE GUEST LIST\NAND NEVER OUTSIDE STANDING ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:41.08.0:13:47.03.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'M LOOKING FOR\NSOMETHING NICE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:50.06.0:13:51.30.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:51.33.0:13:52.87.Default..0.0.0..IS MY VAGINA OUT?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:52.89.0:13:59.34.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:13:59.37.0:14:01.38.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE IN MOM MODE LIKE ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:01.40.0:14:02.61.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. I AM A LITTLE BIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:02.64.0:14:04.98.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. FOR SOME REASON.\NI JUST ALWAYS JUST FALL
Dialogue: 0.0:14:05.01.0:14:06.42.Default..0.0.0..INTO THE MOM ROLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:06.44.0:14:08.35.Default..0.0.0..OH. GOD. BOOBS.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.38.0:14:10.02.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW. I'M JUST\NNOT GONNA DO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:10.05.0:14:12.92.Default..0.0.0..WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.\NWHERE ARE YOU GOING?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:12.95.0:14:14.93.Default..0.0.0..GET A DRINK.\NOKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:14.95.0:14:17.43.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.45.0:14:20.33.Default..0.0.0..CHEERS. TO NOT BEING MOM.\NEXACTLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.36.0:14:21.90.Default..0.0.0..WELL. WE'RE GOING TO END UP\NBEING MOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:21.92.0:14:23.47.Default..0.0.0..LET'S HAVE\NA FUCKING GOOD TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.49.0:14:29.43.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:14:32.20.0:14:33.74.Default..0.0.0..I'M IN THE CLUB\NDOING MY THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:33.77.0:14:35.21.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN I LOOK OVER.\NAND IT LOOKS LIKE
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.24.0:14:37.45.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S ABOUT TO BE\NA FUCKING CRAZY MOSH PIT
Dialogue: 0.0:14:37.47.0:14:38.78.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S JUST RIGHT\NIN FRONT OF ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:38.81.0:14:40.08.Default..0.0.0..UH-OH. UH-OH.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:46.25.0:14:48.03.Default..0.0.0..{bleep} YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:48.05.0:14:49.23.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S THAT MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:49.25.0:14:51.20.Default..0.0.0..THAT MEANS SHAME.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:51.22.0:14:54.23.Default..0.0.0..MIKE IS. LIKE.\NYOU KNOW. SCREAMING.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:54.26.0:14:56.83.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. PUMPING HIS CHEST OUT\NFOR NO REASON.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:56.86.0:14:59.07.Default..0.0.0..YOUR BOY IS FUCKING\NEMBARRASSING.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:59.09.0:15:00.64.Default..0.0.0..IT'S HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:00.66.0:15:03.51.Default..0.0.0..HE'S ACTING TOUGH BECAUSE\NTHERE'S SECURITY RIGHT THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:03.53.0:15:06.68.Default..0.0.0..THE CROWD SAY\N"PIECE OF SHIT."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:06.70.0:15:08.35.Default..0.0.0..MIKE'S ACTING\NLIKE A TOUGH GUY.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:08.37.0:15:10.51.Default..0.0.0..BUT IT'S NOT RIGHT.\NBECAUSE THIS TIME
Dialogue: 0.0:15:10.54.0:15:12.05.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA GET\NEVERYBODY INVOLVED.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:12.07.0:15:14.22.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU'RE READY TO GO.\NI'M READY TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:14.24.0:15:15.82.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCKING EVERY ONE\NOF THESE KIDS UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:15.84.0:15:18.02.Default..0.0.0..I'M READY TO GO RIGHT NOW.\NI DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:18.05.0:15:20.72.Default..0.0.0..THE CROWD'S CHANTING STUFF WITH\NTHAT. "SHAME. SHAME. SHAME."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:20.75.0:15:23.56.Default..0.0.0..BUT I'M HOPING RIGHT NOW\NTHAT SOMEBODY DOES SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:23.59.0:15:27.33.Default..0.0.0..COME ON. TOUGH GUY.\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:27.36.0:15:30.70.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCKING SPLIT\NEVERY ONE OF THESE KIDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:30.73.0:15:32.59.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:34.56.0:15:36.84.Default..0.0.0..DON'T TOUCH ME!\NGO AWAY!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:36.87.0:15:38.14.Default..0.0.0..BACK UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:38.17.0:15:40.28.Default..0.0.0..THEY WERE. LIKE.\NMAKING FUN OF US.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:40.30.0:15:42.61.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:42.64.0:15:44.75.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:44.77.0:15:47.85.Default..0.0.0..DEE. CAN YOU DO THE DISHES?\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:47.88.0:15:49.79.Default..0.0.0..BE A WOMAN!\NDO SOMETHING!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:49.81.0:15:51.41.Default..0.0.0..SHUT THE FUCK UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:54.48.0:15:56.73.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!\NFUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.75.0:15:58.06.Default..0.0.0..COME GET ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:58.09.0:16:00.53.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCK EVERY ONE\NOF THESE KIDS UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:00.56.0:16:03.37.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:03.39.0:16:05.44.Default..0.0.0..STOP.\NNO. CAN'T GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:09.13.0:16:11.91.Default..0.0.0..I SEE YOU. I SEE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:11.93.0:16:13.74.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}MANGIA{\i0} YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:13.77.0:16:15.71.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCKING EAT YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.31.0:16:19.98.Default..0.0.0..CABS ARE HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:24.75.0:16:27.66.Default..0.0.0..I GOT IT. I GOT IT.\NI GOT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:27.68.0:16:29.13.Default..0.0.0..WALK TO THE LEFT?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:29.15.0:16:30.29.Default..0.0.0..STAY BEHIND US.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:35.26.0:16:37.57.Default..0.0.0..STUPID PEOPLE.\NMIKE. STUPID PEOPLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.59.0:16:39.97.Default..0.0.0..MIKE KNOWS THAT THERE ARE\NBOUNCERS IN THE CLUB.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:39.99.0:16:42.21.Default..0.0.0..MIKE ONLY ACTS\NLIKE A TOUGH GUY
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.23.0:16:44.27.Default..0.0.0..WHEN THERE'S PEOPLE AROUND\NTO HOLD BACK THE FIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:44.30.0:16:46.24.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. WATCH OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:46.27.0:16:49.91.Default..0.0.0..OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.94.0:16:51.95.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.\NTIME TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.97.0:16:53.99.Default..0.0.0..THE PLACE IS WACK.\NLET'S GO. BEE-ATCHES.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:54.01.0:16:56.35.Default..0.0.0..I'M INTO GIRLS.\NI'M NOT INTO DRAMA.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:56.38.0:16:57.52.Default..0.0.0..SO I'M READY TO GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.55.0:16:59.02.Default..0.0.0..IT ALMOST GOT CRAZY\NIN THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:59.05.0:17:00.76.Default..0.0.0..BUT I DIDN'T CARE ABOUT NOBODY\NIN THE HOUSE EXCEPT FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:00.78.0:17:01.79.Default..0.0.0..SAME HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:01.82.0:17:05.13.Default..0.0.0..♪ FALL IN.\NDO IT AGAIN ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:05.15.0:17:08.47.Default..0.0.0..♪ LINE UP. EVERYONE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:08.49.0:17:09.93.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:09.96.0:17:12.10.Default..0.0.0..EVERYBODY ELSE RIGHT NOW\NIS JUST LIKE. "LET'S GO HOME."
Dialogue: 0.0:17:12.13.0:17:13.44.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M JUST LIKE. "MEHRR."
Dialogue: 0.0:17:13.46.0:17:15.27.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I'M STILL TRYING\NTO HAVE A GOOD TIME HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:15.30.0:17:16.77.Default..0.0.0..CENTRAL PARK!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:16.80.0:17:19.84.Default..0.0.0..♪ I KNOW 'CAUSE I KNOW\NWHAT I'M THINKING ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:19.87.0:17:23.21.Default..0.0.0..♪ LOVE LIKE OURS\NCOULD NEVER BE BROKEN ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:23.24.0:17:25.78.Default..0.0.0..BYE. SAM.\NBYE. I LOVE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:25.81.0:17:28.82.Default..0.0.0..GET HOME SAFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:28.84.0:17:30.52.Default..0.0.0..MY NIPPLE'S OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:30.55.0:17:32.82.Default..0.0.0..I ONLY KNOW\NI'M GONNA BE MOM
Dialogue: 0.0:17:32.85.0:17:34.19.Default..0.0.0..WHEN I WALK IN CENTRAL PARK.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:34.21.0:17:36.66.Default..0.0.0..SO I'M GOING HOME\NAND GOING TO BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.68.0:17:40.23.Default..0.0.0..♪ LA LA LA LA LA ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:40.26.0:17:42.17.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NI'VE GOTTA PEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:42.19.0:17:45.27.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T RUN FAST ENOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.29.0:17:50.74.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:50.77.0:17:52.28.Default..0.0.0..WHOO!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:52.30.0:17:55.25.Default..0.0.0..YEAH!\NYEAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:55.27.0:17:58.78.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.81.0:18:00.58.Default..0.0.0..STOP SCREAMING IN MY EAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.61.0:18:03.12.Default..0.0.0..IT'S. LIKE. ANNOYING.\NLIKE. GO AWAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.14.0:18:05.02.Default..0.0.0..BACK UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:05.05.0:18:06.72.Default..0.0.0..SO WE'RE TRYING TO DANCE\NAT CENTRAL PARK.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.75.0:18:09.33.Default..0.0.0..AND THESE GUYS ARE. LIKE.\NHARASSING ME AND NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.35.0:18:12.70.Default..0.0.0..I HATE ALL OF YOU. EW!\NBACK UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.72.0:18:14.97.Default..0.0.0..NO. DON'T TOUCH ME!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:14.99.0:18:17.90.Default..0.0.0..GO AWAY!\NBACK UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.93.0:18:20.91.Default..0.0.0..DO YOUR OWN THING.\NGO.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:20.93.0:18:23.24.Default..0.0.0..THEY WERE. LIKE.\NMAKING FUN OF US.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:23.26.0:18:25.81.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE IT WAS THE BOOTS.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:25.83.0:18:27.78.Default..0.0.0..WHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:27.80.0:18:30.01.Default..0.0.0..SO FUCKING STUPID.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:34.64.0:18:36.59.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE THAT WAS MATURE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.61.0:18:40.12.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS VERY MATURE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.15.0:18:41.86.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:41.88.0:18:43.53.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:43.55.0:18:47.36.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!\NWHOA. WHOA. WHOA!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:47.39.0:18:49.53.Default..0.0.0..THROWING ICE AT ME\NAND MY FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:49.56.0:18:50.77.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T FUCKING DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:50.79.0:18:52.87.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:52.89.0:18:55.07.Default..0.0.0..DONE. DONE!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:55.10.0:18:58.31.Default..0.0.0..FUCKING DEAD!\NI DON'T REALLY GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:58.33.0:19:00.88.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK..\NDEENA. IT'S FINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.90.0:19:01.88.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK..
Dialogue: 0.0:19:01.90.0:19:03.21.Default..0.0.0..DEENA. IT'S FINE.\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:03.24.0:19:05.58.Default..0.0.0..GET ME OUT OF HERE. BECAUSE\NI'M GONNA GO BACK THERE
Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.61.0:19:07.52.Default..0.0.0..AND FUCK THEM UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:07.54.0:19:09.75.Default..0.0.0..I FUCKING WISH. BRO.\NLISTEN. LISTEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:09.78.0:19:11.15.Default..0.0.0..I WISH. BRO.\NLISTEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:11.18.0:19:12.46.Default..0.0.0..THAT WASN'T RIGHT\NFOR THEM TO DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.48.0:19:13.79.Default..0.0.0..THEY'RE FUCKING ASSHOLES.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:13.82.0:19:17.03.Default..0.0.0..WE ACTUALLY PROVED THAT WE\NACTUALLY HAVE MANNERS.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:17.05.0:19:21.47.Default..0.0.0..AND WE ACTUALLY HAVE. LIKE.\NRESPECT FOR OTHER PEOPLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:21.49.0:19:25.20.Default..0.0.0..EVERYONE'S GONNA SEE ME AND I\NLOOK LIKE A TWO-CENT HOOKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:26.33.0:19:28.81.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK PHENOMENAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:28.83.0:19:30.79.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE SO OUT OF OUR ELEMENT.\NIT'S SICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:39.51.0:19:41.15.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU. ASSHOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:41.18.0:19:42.49.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T REALLY GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.51.0:19:45.39.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.41.0:19:47.36.Default..0.0.0..HE THREW A FUCKING ICE CUBE\NAT ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:47.38.0:19:48.56.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU THINK\NI'M GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.58.0:19:50.56.Default..0.0.0..ME TOO. I HAVE AN ICE CUBE\NIN MY BAG.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:50.59.0:19:52.90.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE AN ICE CUBE IN\NMY FUCKING BAG RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.92.0:19:54.23.Default..0.0.0..HE THREW A BOWL\NOF ICE CUBES AT US.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:54.26.0:19:55.77.Default..0.0.0..LUCKILY.\NTHERE WAS SECURITY THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:55.79.0:19:58.27.Default..0.0.0..SCUMBAG!\NYOU SCUMBAG FUCK!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:58.29.0:20:00.74.Default..0.0.0..I WILL FUCK YOU UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:00.76.0:20:02.87.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T EVEN FUCKING CARE!\NCALM DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:02.90.0:20:06.18.Default..0.0.0..ANGRY DEENA COMES STORMING\NTHROUGH THE HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:06.20.0:20:08.18.Default..0.0.0..I'M JUST LIKE.\NWHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:08.20.0:20:10.25.Default..0.0.0..THAT FUCKING BARTENDER\NTHREW ICE CUBES AT US.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:10.27.0:20:12.12.Default..0.0.0..A BARTENDER THREW ICE?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:12.14.0:20:13.62.Default..0.0.0..HE WAS THROWING EVERYTHING\NAT US.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:13.64.0:20:16.29.Default..0.0.0..THREW ICE AT US.\NA DRINK. EVERYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.31.0:20:18.06.Default..0.0.0..THE BARTENDER?\NYES.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:18.08.0:20:20.69.Default..0.0.0..AND ME AND DEE WERE LIKE.\N"BYE!"
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.72.0:20:22.53.Default..0.0.0..AND I WAS LIKE.\N"FUCK YOU. YOU FUCKING DICK."
Dialogue: 0.0:20:22.55.0:20:23.83.Default..0.0.0..WE COULDN'T DEFEND\NOURSELVES.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.85.0:20:25.10.Default..0.0.0..THE MEATBALLS ARE DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:25.12.0:20:27.30.Default..0.0.0..AND I FEEL LIKE I'M IN\NA SNOOPY EPISODE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:27.32.0:20:29.00.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE ALL YOU HEAR IS.\N"MMRR MMRR MMRR MMRR
Dialogue: 0.0:20:29.02.0:20:31.04.Default..0.0.0..MMRR MMRR MMRR. MMRR MMRR\NMMRR MMRR MMRR MMRR MMRR."
Dialogue: 0.0:20:31.06.0:20:32.44.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M JUST LIKE.\NF-M-L.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.46.0:20:36.07.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU SAW THAT. JENNI.\NYOU WOULD THROW BLOWS.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.10.0:20:37.14.Default..0.0.0..SAM. YOU WOULD THROW BLOWS.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:37.17.0:20:38.14.Default..0.0.0..YOU WOULD HAVE THROWN\NSO MANY BLOWS.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.17.0:20:39.24.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS HORRIBLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:39.27.0:20:41.41.Default..0.0.0..YOU JUST ARE\NWORKED UP RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.44.0:20:43.01.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE JUST WORKED UP.\NYEAH. CALM DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.04.0:20:44.08.Default..0.0.0..YOU JUST GOTTA...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:44.11.0:20:45.32.Default..0.0.0..AND THIS IS WHY I AM\NTHE WAY I AM.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.34.0:20:46.52.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE YOU KNOW IT.\NJENNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:46.54.0:20:49.05.Default..0.0.0..WHEN YOU GET\NFUCKING SOUPED-UP
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.08.0:20:50.75.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU WANT TO FUCKING\NKNOCK SOMEONE OUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:50.78.0:20:52.19.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NTELL ME HOW YOU FEEL.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.21.0:20:54.26.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE AND DEENA\NARE SO INSANE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:54.28.0:20:56.36.Default..0.0.0..I WILL FUCKING\NKNOCK SOMEONE OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.38.0:20:58.93.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANT NOTHING\NTO DO WITH THEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.95.0:21:01.47.Default..0.0.0..ODDLY ENOUGH. I WOULD RATHER\NHANG OUT WITH SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:01.49.0:21:02.90.Default..0.0.0..GO FIGURE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:02.92.0:21:04.74.Default..0.0.0..NEGATIVE ENERGY.\NNEGATIVE. NEGATIVE ENERGY.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:04.76.0:21:06.14.Default..0.0.0..I JUST THINK THEY'RE ALL...
Dialogue: 0.0:21:06.16.0:21:07.97.Default..0.0.0..THEY'VE BEEN DRINKING ALL DAY.\NTHEY'RE HYPED.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:08.00.0:21:10.11.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T TAKE IT\NON A DAILY BASIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:10.13.0:21:13.01.Default..0.0.0..I CAN FUCKING KNOCK SOMEONE\NOUT. EVEN THOUGH I'M SMALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.03.0:21:14.91.Default..0.0.0..I GET IT. RELAX.\NI KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.94.0:21:16.45.Default..0.0.0..I JUST HAVE TO BREATHE.\NJUST BREATHE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:16.47.0:21:17.45.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO BREATHE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:17.47.0:21:18.78.Default..0.0.0..BREATHE.\NTHAT'S IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:18.81.0:21:20.42.Default..0.0.0..MEATBALL PROBLEMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:20.44.0:21:24.55.Default..0.0.0..DUDE. LET'S GO INSIDE.\NYOU READY FOR A HOT TUB?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:24.58.0:21:27.66.Default..0.0.0..BEING KICKED OUT OF THE CLUB.\NMEATBALL PROBLEMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:27.68.0:21:29.16.Default..0.0.0..DEENA!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:29.18.0:21:31.43.Default..0.0.0..SHOULD WE GO IN?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:31.45.0:21:36.10.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING IN WITH CLOTHES IN...\NCLOTHES ON... BECAUSE I'M FAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:36.12.0:21:39.50.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO PEE.\NYOU COULD PEE IN THE HOT TUB.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:39.53.0:21:41.27.Default..0.0.0..♪ HOO HOO ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:21:41.30.0:21:43.67.Default..0.0.0..AAH! IT'S. LIKE.\NBURNING MY SKIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.70.0:21:44.94.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T EVEN GET IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:44.97.0:21:48.85.Default..0.0.0..BURNING YOUR CUCA IN A JACUZZI.\NMEATBALL PROBLEMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:48.87.0:21:50.25.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE WORST PAIN\NIN THE WORLD.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:50.27.0:21:51.65.Default..0.0.0..OH. I'M GETTING USED TO IT.\NTHOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:51.67.0:21:53.92.Default..0.0.0..OOH. I KIND OF LIKE IT.\NOH. WAIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:53.94.0:21:58.89.Default..0.0.0..MEATBALLS ARE BURNING UP\NIN THIS THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:58.91.0:22:00.96.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO FUCKING HOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:00.98.0:22:04.63.Default..0.0.0..♪ YOU GET MY LOVE ♪\N♪ WHOA WHOA WHOA ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:04.65.0:22:06.00.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T EVEN KNOW\NWHAT TIME IT IS.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:06.02.0:22:09.17.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL LIKE IT'S EARLY\NBECAUSE THE SUN'S UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:09.19.0:22:11.87.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GO OUT. IT'S AWESOME.\NCAN YOU GO OUT AGAIN?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:11.89.0:22:14.57.Default..0.0.0..DUDE. WE CAN KILL IT\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:14.60.0:22:16.97.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCKING GO OUT.\NWE CAN KILL IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:20.00.0:22:27.94.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:29.31.0:22:32.49.Default..0.0.0..READY?\NOF COURSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:32.51.0:22:35.13.Default..0.0.0..EVERYONE'S GONNA SEE ME AND I\NLOOK LIKE A TWO-CENT HOOKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:35.15.0:22:37.23.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK LIKE A HOOKER?\NSO DO I.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:37.25.0:22:39.63.Default..0.0.0..NO SHIT.\NWHERE ARE WE EVEN GOING?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:39.65.0:22:41.40.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:41.42.0:22:44.27.Default..0.0.0..WE CAN JUST WALK AROUND.\NTHAT'S WHAT I'M SAYING.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.29.0:22:47.34.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK FUCKING PHENOMENAL.\NWE'RE JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:47.36.0:22:52.04.Default..0.0.0..YOU WISH YOU LOOKED LIKE THIS\NAT 7:30 IN THE MORNING.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:55.04.0:22:57.41.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE SO OUT OF OUR ELEMENT.\NIT'S SICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:59.91.0:23:02.29.Default..0.0.0..SHUT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.31.0:23:05.98.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE NOT HOOKERS.\NWE'RE JUST JERSEY. GET IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:12.22.0:23:14.56.Default..0.0.0..AT THIS POINT.\NWE'RE TAN GIRL WASTED.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:14.59.0:23:16.90.Default..0.0.0..AND WE WANT TO BE\NMEATBALL WASTED.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:16.92.0:23:19.74.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA CRASH A LITTLE BIT.\NBUT ALCOHOL CURES IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:19.76.0:23:21.77.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE MEMORIAL DAY\NWEEKEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:21.80.0:23:25.01.Default..0.0.0..EVEN THOUGH WE'RE FUCKING TIRED\NAND WE HAVEN'T SLEPT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:25.03.0:23:27.61.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA BE FINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:27.63.0:23:30.48.Default..0.0.0..MEATBALL POWER. THAT'S IT.\NMEATBALL POWER.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:30.50.0:23:32.38.Default..0.0.0..JUST THINK OF IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:32.41.0:23:34.68.Default..0.0.0..DUDE. WE'RE LIVING\NOUR FRICKIN' LIVES.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:34.71.0:23:36.52.Default..0.0.0..I'M DYING.\NSTAND UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:36.54.0:23:38.62.Default..0.0.0..I'M DRUNK.\NNO. I KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:38.65.0:23:42.26.Default..0.0.0..CAN'T I JUST SLEEP FOR TWO\NSECONDS AND THEN WE'LL GO PLAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.28.0:23:44.36.Default..0.0.0..OKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:44.39.0:23:49.10.Default..0.0.0..I'M GONNA TAKE A NAP.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:52.13.0:23:58.06.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:24:00.84.0:24:03.45.Default..0.0.0..♪ WHEN I WAS YOUNG. KID.\NI THOUGHT TO MYSELF ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:24:03.47.0:24:06.18.Default..0.0.0..♪ THAT I COULD SHAKE THE WORLD\NAND WIN MY MONEY BACK ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:24:06.21.0:24:07.35.Default..0.0.0..WALK OF SHAME.\NYEAH. BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:07.37.0:24:10.65.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. SHUT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:10.68.0:24:12.72.Default..0.0.0..HOLY LEOPARD SKIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:12.75.0:24:15.93.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO THEY PUT IN THE ALCOHOL\NIN THIS COUNTRY?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:15.95.0:24:18.26.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S GOTTA BE SOMETHING\NDIFFERENT
Dialogue: 0.0:24:18.29.0:24:19.93.Default..0.0.0..IN THE ALCOHOL OUT HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:19.95.0:24:21.65.Default..0.0.0..FUCK MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:25.19.0:24:27.84.Default..0.0.0..♪ YEAH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:24:27.86.0:24:30.64.Default..0.0.0..♪ OH. YEAH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:24:30.66.0:24:31.88.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:31.90.0:24:33.71.Default..0.0.0..SO TONIGHT. WE DECIDE\NWE'RE GONNA BARBECUE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:33.73.0:24:35.65.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE WE'RE OVER THE PASTA\NAND THE PIZZA.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:35.67.0:24:37.05.Default..0.0.0..THE HELL?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:40.54.0:24:42.02.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO I DO ABOUT THIS?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:42.04.0:24:46.56.Default..0.0.0..WOW! FIRE. FIRE. FIRE!\NFIRE. FIRE. FIRE. FIRE!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:46.58.0:24:48.46.Default..0.0.0..WITH ME IN THE HOUSE. YOU DON'T\NNEED A FIRE ALARM.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:48.48.0:24:49.59.Default..0.0.0..I WAS THE FIRE ALARM.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:49.62.0:24:52.86.Default..0.0.0..FIRE. FIRE. FIRE!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:52.89.0:24:55.57.Default..0.0.0..FIRE. FIRE. FIRE! FIRE!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:55.59.0:24:57.20.Default..0.0.0..RON. BE CAREFUL.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:57.22.0:24:58.54.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL LIKE A FIREMAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:58.56.0:25:00.24.Default..0.0.0..AND FAT WOMEN ARE JUMPING\NON MY TRAMPOLINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:00.26.0:25:01.64.Default..0.0.0..I'M JUST LIKE.\N"THAT'S WHAT'S UP."
Dialogue: 0.0:25:01.66.0:25:03.27.Default..0.0.0..THE FUCKING THING\NJUST WENT UP IN FLAMES.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:03.30.0:25:04.54.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:04.57.0:25:06.24.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS THE BEST DAY\NOF MY LIFE ON THE GRILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:06.27.0:25:08.45.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE A GOOD BARBECUE\NTHIS TIME OF YEAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:08.47.0:25:10.31.Default..0.0.0..♪ IT'S BURNING UP\NIN HERE. BABY ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:10.34.0:25:11.75.Default..0.0.0..I BURNED THE BARBECUE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:11.77.0:25:14.52.Default..0.0.0..SO NOW I HAVE TO GO GROCERY\NSHOPPING FOR SUNDAY DINNER.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:14.54.0:25:15.89.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU WANT TO GO SHOPPING?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:15.91.0:25:18.22.Default..0.0.0..SHOP? MAYBE. LIKE.\NMEN'S AND WOMEN'S STORES?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:18.25.0:25:19.62.Default..0.0.0..JUST GET FOOD FOR THE HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:19.65.0:25:22.13.Default..0.0.0..OH. MAN. I'M FUCKING AM GOING\NGROCERY SHOPPING AGAIN?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:22.15.0:25:24.79.Default..0.0.0..YEP. WHIPPING YOU\NINTO SHAPE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:24.82.0:25:27.80.Default..0.0.0..♪ SHE'S ON FIRE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:27.82.0:25:30.20.Default..0.0.0..♪ SHE'S SMOKIN' HOT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:30.22.0:25:32.37.Default..0.0.0..♪ MY GIRLFRIEND\NIS A SCORCHER ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:32.39.0:25:35.91.Default..0.0.0..♪ MAN. SHE'LL BURN DOWN\NTHIS SPOT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:35.93.0:25:39.01.Default..0.0.0..IT'S SUNDAY NIGHT.\NAND I'M GONNA TRY AND MAKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:39.03.0:25:41.18.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. MY OWN SAUSAGE AND PEPPERS\NFOR EVERYBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:41.20.0:25:43.21.Default..0.0.0..CIAO.\NCIAO.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:43.24.0:25:44.21.Default..0.0.0..♪ SHE'S A HOT TAMALE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:44.24.0:25:46.98.Default..0.0.0..♪ SHE'S A HOT TAMALE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:47.01.0:25:49.29.Default..0.0.0..♪ SHE'S A HOT\NTAMALE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:49.31.0:25:52.36.Default..0.0.0..♪ SHE'S A HOT TAMALE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:52.38.0:25:53.36.Default..0.0.0..♪ UHH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:25:53.38.0:25:56.12.Default..0.0.0..YOU WENT SHOPPING?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:02.72.0:26:04.40.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK PRETTY.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:04.43.0:26:06.60.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?\NYOU LOOK PRETTY.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:06.63.0:26:07.80.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}GRAZIE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:07.83.0:26:09.71.Default..0.0.0..CAN SOMEONE DO THE DISHES?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:09.73.0:26:12.68.Default..0.0.0..DEE. COULD YOU DO THE DISHES?\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:12.70.0:26:15.31.Default..0.0.0..SHE NEVER-\NSHE NEVER DOES ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:15.34.0:26:17.75.Default..0.0.0..I NEVER DO ANYTHING. MIKE?\NI NEVER SEE YOU DO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:17.77.0:26:19.02.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU FUCKING KIDDING ME?\NMAYBE YOU SHOULD...
Dialogue: 0.0:26:19.04.0:26:20.42.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU EVER CLEAN?\NDO YOU EVER COOK?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:20.44.0:26:21.99.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T STAND YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:22.01.0:26:23.39.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T LIKE YOU.\NI DON'T LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:23.41.0:26:25.36.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T LIKE YOU EITHER.\NDO SOME DISHES.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:25.38.0:26:27.59.Default..0.0.0..DO SOME DISHES.\NBE A WOMAN!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:27.61.0:26:29.36.Default..0.0.0..DO SOMETHING!\NSHUT THE FUCK UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:31.52.0:26:33.30.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T LIVE WITH\NTHAT {bleep} DOUCHE BAG.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:33.32.0:26:34.80.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT FUCKING\NLIVING WITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:34.82.0:26:36.03.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW PEOPLE\NDON'T LIKE YOU
Dialogue: 0.0:26:36.06.0:26:37.50.Default..0.0.0..FOR YOU TO GET PUNCHED\NIN THE FACE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:37.52.0:26:39.50.Default..0.0.0..A CHAMPAGNE BOTTLE THROWN\NAT YOUR HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:39.53.0:26:41.51.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN SPATULAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:41.53.0:26:43.24.Default..0.0.0..MIKE'S STUCK\NIN THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:43.26.0:26:44.77.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:44.80.0:26:47.44.Default..0.0.0..SOMEBODY WANT TO HELP ME?\N'CAUSE I'M LOCKED IN HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:47.47.0:26:49.88.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW. IT'S LIKE.\NWELL. FUCKING LEAVE HIM THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:49.90.0:26:51.45.Default..0.0.0..I REALLY DON'T WANT TO\NKICK IT DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:51.47.0:26:53.41.Default..0.0.0..I WILL KICK IT DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:55.04.0:26:56.99.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU EVER CLEAN?\NDO YOU EVER COOK?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:57.01.0:26:59.49.Default..0.0.0..I DO. ACTUALLY. MIKE!\NBE A WOMAN!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:59.51.0:27:02.56.Default..0.0.0..DO SOMETHING!\NSHUT THE FUCK UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:02.58.0:27:05.13.Default..0.0.0..DON'T MAKE ME GO LOW-BLOW.\NI WILL. I WILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:05.15.0:27:07.76.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. I'M FAT? I'M FAT?\NYOU WANT TO CALL ME FAT. MIKE?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:07.79.0:27:09.70.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE THAT'S WHAT YOU CALL\NEVERY WOMAN!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:09.72.0:27:11.37.Default..0.0.0..I CAN LOSE WEIGHT FOR FREE!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:11.39.0:27:15.41.Default..0.0.0..YOU NEED ABOUT 10 GRAND\NTO FIX YOUR FUCKING FACE!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:15.43.0:27:17.31.Default..0.0.0..DO YOUR THING. GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:17.33.0:27:18.41.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T REALLY CARE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:18.43.0:27:20.11.Default..0.0.0..I THINK THE MEATBALLS\NSHOULD JUMP HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:20.13.0:27:21.24.Default..0.0.0..DIDN'T YOU JUST TELL ME\NHE WAS YOUR BEST FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:21.27.0:27:22.35.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. TWO DAYS AGO?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:22.37.0:27:23.88.Default..0.0.0..NO. THAT'S NOT WHAT HAPPENED.\NVINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:23.90.0:27:25.18.Default..0.0.0..I'M KIDDING YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:25.21.0:27:26.32.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS HAVE GOT TO\NGET YOUR FUCKING STORY STRAIGHT
Dialogue: 0.0:27:26.34.0:27:28.09.Default..0.0.0..BEFORE YOU GET A SPATULA\NTHROWN AT YOUR HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:28.11.0:27:29.79.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW PEOPLE DON'T\NLIKE YOU IF EVERY DAY
Dialogue: 0.0:27:29.81.0:27:32.12.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA GET PUNCHED\NIN THE FACE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:32.15.0:27:33.89.Default..0.0.0..YOU HAVE TO RUN\NINTO A WALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:33.91.0:27:35.96.Default..0.0.0..A CHAMPAGNE BOTTLE THROWN\NAT YOUR HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:35.98.0:27:37.83.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN SPATULAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:44.43.0:27:47.20.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE COOKING RIGHT NOW.\N{\i1}SCUSI.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:27:47.23.0:27:49.34.Default..0.0.0..SAM'S COOKING IN A DRESS\NSHE WOULD NEVER WEAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:51.20.0:27:52.54.Default..0.0.0..BITCH. YOU'RE GONNA\NDO DISHES.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:53.97.0:27:55.88.Default..0.0.0..ME AND JENNI. WE NORMALLY DON'T\NALWAYS GET ALONG.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:55.90.0:27:57.58.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE WE'RE BOTH.\NLIKE. A LITTLE BIT...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:57.60.0:27:58.85.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE BOTH BITCHES.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:58.87.0:28:00.42.Default..0.0.0..WHO WOULD HAVE THOUGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:00.44.0:28:02.22.Default..0.0.0..ME AND SAM COOKING\NSUNDAY DINNER TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:02.24.0:28:04.42.Default..0.0.0..PRETTY MUCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:04.45.0:28:07.69.Default..0.0.0..TWO ENEMIES ARE NOW. LIKE.\NACTUALLY BEING COOL
Dialogue: 0.0:28:07.71.0:28:08.93.Default..0.0.0..AND COOKING\NNEXT TO EACH OTHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:08.95.0:28:10.93.Default..0.0.0..ABOUT THAT TIME\NTO SIT DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:10.95.0:28:13.16.Default..0.0.0..I'M BRINGING MY BALLS\NTO DINNER.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:13.19.0:28:15.10.Default..0.0.0..MEATBALL PROBLEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:15.12.0:28:17.00.Default..0.0.0..EW. I HATE HEARING THAT.\NME TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:17.02.0:28:20.14.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO OVER IT.\NIT'S THE WAY IT'S SAID.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:20.16.0:28:22.61.Default..0.0.0..ODDLY ENOUGH.\NIN BETWEEN THE FIGHTING.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:22.63.0:28:24.74.Default..0.0.0..ME AND SAM WERE ABLE TO DEVELOP\NA BETTER FRIENDSHIP
Dialogue: 0.0:28:24.76.0:28:26.41.Default..0.0.0..THAT I NEVER THOUGHT I WOULD\NHAVE WITH HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:26.43.0:28:28.95.Default..0.0.0..OUR LAST SUNDAY DINNER\NIN ITALY.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:28.97.0:28:32.08.Default..0.0.0..IT SMELLS PHENOMENAL!\NCAN I HAVE THE TORTELLINI?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:32.11.0:28:35.25.Default..0.0.0..ENJOY. GUYS.\NI HOPE YOU LIKE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:35.28.0:28:36.65.Default..0.0.0..CAN YOU PASS ME\NTHE HAIR SPRAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:37.98.0:28:39.99.Default..0.0.0..DON'T FUCKING PUT IT\NIN YOUR MOUTH. PLEASE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:40.01.0:28:41.22.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT I TOLD HIM.\NIT TASTES GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:41.25.0:28:42.76.Default..0.0.0..I'VE NEVER COOKED BEFORE.\NLIKE. COME ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:42.78.0:28:44.33.Default..0.0.0..NO. IT'S GOOD. I TASTED IT.\NIT'S GOOD?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:44.35.0:28:45.93.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. IT'S ACTUALLY GOOD.\NTHANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:45.95.0:28:49.07.Default..0.0.0..OKAY. LAST SUNDAY DINNER.\NLET'S DO A TOAST.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:49.09.0:28:51.73.Default..0.0.0..I HAD A GOOD TIME OUT HERE.\NLIKE. I LOVE ITALY.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:51.76.0:28:54.07.Default..0.0.0..I HAD SOME OF THE BEST DAYS\NOF MY LIFE OUT HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:54.09.0:28:56.21.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NI THINK THAT. BEING HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:56.23.0:28:58.24.Default..0.0.0..WE CAN REALLY APPRECIATE WHAT\NWE'RE GONNA HAVE
Dialogue: 0.0:28:58.27.0:29:00.04.Default..0.0.0..BACK IN JERSEY. YOU KNOW?\NSO...
Dialogue: 0.0:29:00.07.0:29:02.91.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUDDY.\NI'M GLAD WE'RE LEAVING.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:05.94.0:29:07.15.Default..0.0.0..ME TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:07.17.0:29:08.99.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE IT OUT HERE.\NBUT IT'S GOOD TO VISIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:09.01.0:29:10.39.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NI'M READY TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:10.41.0:29:11.52.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO GO TANNING.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:11.55.0:29:12.96.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. IMAGINE WALKING\NINTO KARMA.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:12.98.0:29:14.59.Default..0.0.0..AND IT'LL BE LIKE.\N"WHOO!"
Dialogue: 0.0:29:14.61.0:29:15.99.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW.\NBEING HERE IN ITALY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:16.02.0:29:19.86.Default..0.0.0..OBVIOUSLY IT'S BEAUTIFUL.\NBUT I JUST MISS THE SHORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:19.89.0:29:21.16.Default..0.0.0..AND WE'RE GOING BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:21.19.0:29:23.53.Default..0.0.0..I LOVED ITALY.\NIT WAS A GREAT EXPERIENCE HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:23.56.0:29:25.67.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T HAVE ANY ISSUES\NWITH THE HOUSEHOLD.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:25.69.0:29:27.34.Default..0.0.0..AND I FELT PRETTY\NFUCKING GOOD ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:27.36.0:29:30.01.Default..0.0.0..FOR ONCE. RON AND SAM\NHAVEN'T BEEN IN A FIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:30.03.0:29:31.91.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW. I KNOW. THAT'S\NWHY I'M KNOCKING ON WOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:31.93.0:29:33.74.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GIVE A ROUND OF APPLAUSE\NFOR RON AND SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:35.34.0:29:36.61.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE EVERYBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:36.64.0:29:38.41.Default..0.0.0..THANK YOU ALL FOR. LIKE.\NI DON'T KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:38.44.0:29:40.18.Default..0.0.0..BEING COOL AND FRIENDS.\NAND I HOPE IN JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:40.21.0:29:41.65.Default..0.0.0..WE CAN ALL REMAIN THIS WAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:41.68.0:29:44.49.Default..0.0.0..YES.\NLET'S HAVE FUN IN JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:44.51.0:29:46.02.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}SALUD.{\i0}\NYEAH. BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:46.05.0:29:48.22.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUDDY. WE'RE GOING TO\NJERSEY. YEAH. BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:48.25.0:29:49.73.Default..0.0.0..WHOO!\NTASTES LIKE COUGH SYRUP.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:49.75.0:29:51.29.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK WAS THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:51.32.0:29:53.50.Default..0.0.0..NO. IT DOESN'T. I WILL DRINK\NTHE WHOLE FRICKIN' BOTTLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:53.52.0:29:56.40.Default..0.0.0..I LIKE YOU GUYS.\NBUT I DON'T CARE
Dialogue: 0.0:29:56.42.0:29:57.83.Default..0.0.0..WHAT YOU GUYS SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:57.86.0:30:01.34.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING INTO MY ROOM\NBACK IN JERSEY
Dialogue: 0.0:30:01.36.0:30:02.91.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M PUTTING MY BAG THERE
Dialogue: 0.0:30:02.93.0:30:05.07.Default..0.0.0..AND THAT'S MY ROOM.\NAND THAT'S IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:05.10.0:30:06.31.Default..0.0.0..WHY... WHY... WHO ARE YOU TO SAY\NTHAT THAT'S YOUR ROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:06.33.0:30:08.38.Default..0.0.0..HOW IS THAT NOT MY ROOM?\NTELL ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:08.40.0:30:11.58.Default..0.0.0..FOR ME. I DON'T THINK UPSTAIRS\NIS A GOOD PLACE FOR ME ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:11.61.0:30:14.12.Default..0.0.0..AND TO GO DOWNSTAIRS\NWOULD BE EASIER ON ME. LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:30:14.14.0:30:15.25.Default..0.0.0..SWITCH WITH SOMEBODY ELSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:15.28.0:30:16.72.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S MY ROOM.\NI WANT TO KEEP MY ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:16.74.0:30:18.35.Default..0.0.0..I AM THINKING. LIKE.\NLET'S COME UP
Dialogue: 0.0:30:18.38.0:30:20.82.Default..0.0.0..WITH SOME KIND OF\N"COMPROMISATION" ON THIS ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:20.85.0:30:23.33.Default..0.0.0..AND VIN IS JUST BEING\NA COMPLETE LITTLE BITCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:23.35.0:30:25.39.Default..0.0.0..WHY CAN'T YOU. PAULY. AND MIKE\NGET A ROOM TOGETHER?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:25.42.0:30:28.80.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE MIKE BRINGS DRAMA INTO\NDIFFERENT SITUATIONS.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:28.82.0:30:29.80.Default..0.0.0..AND WE'RE NOT LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:29.82.0:30:31.40.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE DRAMA-FREE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:31.42.0:30:34.50.Default..0.0.0..HEY. YEAH. YEAH. WELL-\NI MEAN. WHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:34.53.0:30:36.54.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT TO SLEEP\NON THE COUCH DOWNSTAIRS...
Dialogue: 0.0:30:36.56.0:30:38.51.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T CARE. SO PUT ME\NWHEREVER YOU WANT ME TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:38.53.0:30:39.51.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T CARE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:39.53.0:30:40.84.Default..0.0.0..VINNY'S JUST A YOUNG KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.87.0:30:44.48.Default..0.0.0..SO WHEN A LITTLE DRAMA\NGETS TO VINNY. HE SHUTS DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:44.50.0:30:46.42.Default..0.0.0..WHEN DRAMA GETS TO ME.\NI GET UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:46.44.0:30:48.72.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE ONLY TWO-BEDROOM.\NAND?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:48.74.0:30:51.49.Default..0.0.0..WE HAVE A GREAT THING.\NYOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:51.51.0:30:54.32.Default..0.0.0..AND WE SLEEP IN THAT ROOM-\NSOMETIMES TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:54.35.0:30:56.23.Default..0.0.0..SOMETIMES TOGETHER.\NWHATEVER. VIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:56.25.0:30:57.43.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. DO WHAT\NYOU GOTTA DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:57.45.0:30:59.10.Default..0.0.0..JUST IT'S FUCKING BULLSHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:59.12.0:31:00.80.Default..0.0.0..FIGHT ME FOR IT.\NLIKE. YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:00.82.0:31:04.30.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S LIKE THE FUCKING\NIMMATURE FUCKING BULLSHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:04.32.0:31:05.90.Default..0.0.0..YOU ALL RIGHT?\NNO. YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:05.93.0:31:06.97.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T FUCKING\NSAY ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:06.99.0:31:08.30.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU WANT ME\NTO SAY TO HIM?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:08.33.0:31:09.54.Default..0.0.0..I'M THE ONLY ONE SCREAMING\NAT THE FUCKING KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:09.56.0:31:10.57.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO-\NWHAT. DO YOU WANT TO
Dialogue: 0.0:31:10.60.0:31:12.21.Default..0.0.0..FIGHT THE KID\NOVER A FUCKING ROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:12.23.0:31:14.88.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T LIVE WITH THAT FUCKING\NDOUCHE BAG IN THAT ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:14.90.0:31:17.68.Default..0.0.0..IT'S. LIKE. BAD LUCK.\NYOU'RE GONNA GET MAD AT ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:17.71.0:31:19.25.Default..0.0.0..JUST LEAVE ME ALONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:19.27.0:31:22.42.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT FUCKING ROOMING\NWITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:22.44.0:31:23.99.Default..0.0.0..NOBODY WANTS TO ROOM\NWITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:24.01.0:31:25.92.Default..0.0.0..WE SHOULD JUST\NFUCKING PUT MIKE SOMEWHERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:25.95.0:31:28.93.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. IN THE GARBAGE CAN.\NWHY DON'T WE JUST SAY THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:28.95.0:31:30.03.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE YOU CAN'T DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:30.05.0:31:32.60.Default..0.0.0..MIKE SHOULD JUST\NTAKE THE FREAKIN' COUCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:32.62.0:31:34.66.Default..0.0.0..OOH. SECRETS.\NDISCUSSING.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:34.69.0:31:37.43.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE JUST SAYING THAT\NI COULD NEVER LIVE WITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:38.83.0:31:41.44.Default..0.0.0..WHY ARE YOU LAUGHING?\NLIKE. I'M BEING SERIOUS.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:41.46.0:31:43.51.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS ARE NOT REALLY GONNA\NHAVE TO WORRY ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:43.53.0:31:46.84.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I PROBABLY\NAM NOT GOING TO JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:46.87.0:31:50.88.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT TO LEAVE. BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:50.90.0:31:52.35.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T WANT TO FUCK\NWITH ME. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:52.37.0:31:53.85.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T WANT TO DO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:53.87.0:31:56.39.Default..0.0.0..LATELY. MIKE'S BEEN DOING\NNOTHING BUT STARTING PROBLEMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:56.41.0:31:58.19.Default..0.0.0..I'LL EAT YOU.\NMOTHERFUCKER..
Dialogue: 0.0:31:58.21.0:32:00.69.Default..0.0.0..IF MIKE GETS INTO A FIGHT.\NI'M NOT GONNA JUMP IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:00.71.0:32:03.11.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GO.\NOH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:06.29.0:32:08.43.Default..0.0.0..I PROBABLY\NAM NOT GOING TO JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:08.46.0:32:11.27.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT TO LEAVE. BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:11.29.0:32:14.04.Default..0.0.0..I'M TIRED OF FIGHTING.\NI'M TIRED OF IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:14.06.0:32:16.67.Default..0.0.0..DUDE. ARE YOU KIDDING ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:16.70.0:32:18.51.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T CONSIDER YOU A FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.53.0:32:20.98.Default..0.0.0..DUDE. EVERYBODY IN THE HOUSE\NAGREES WITH US.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:21.00.0:32:21.98.Default..0.0.0..EVEN IF THEY DON'T SAY IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.00.0:32:23.38.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'D YOU SAY. SNOOKS?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:23.40.0:32:24.81.Default..0.0.0..I THOUGHT YOU WERE DIFFERENT\NAND YOU'RE NOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:24.84.0:32:26.22.Default..0.0.0..I AM DIFFERENT.\NNO. YOU'RE NOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:26.24.0:32:29.95.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A DICK.\NNO. I'M NOT A DICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:29.98.0:32:32.96.Default..0.0.0..I JUST... I JUST DON'T KNOW HOW TO\NTAKE THE HIGH ROAD LIKE YOU DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:32.98.0:32:34.82.Default..0.0.0..YOU ALWAYS TAKE\NTHE FUCKING EXPRESS LANE.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:34.85.0:32:37.56.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUT I'M NOT PERFECT.\NI GOT MY ISSUES TOO. YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:37.58.0:32:39.96.Default..0.0.0..YOU JUST DEAL WITH IT\NA LOT BETTER THAN I DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:39.99.0:32:41.92.Default..0.0.0..NO FLASH.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:49.56.0:32:51.47.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T REALLY HAVE ISSUES\NWITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:51.50.0:32:54.74.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA HAVE AN ISSUE NOW\NOVER A FUCKING BEDROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:54.77.0:32:56.88.Default..0.0.0..IF I HAVE TO LIVE WITH MIKE.\NI'LL TELL YOU RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:56.90.0:32:58.35.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA BE IN THAT ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.37.0:33:01.65.Default..0.0.0..I THINK THAT'S LIKE WHY-\NNO SHIT. NO SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:01.68.0:33:03.79.Default..0.0.0..WHEN I SEPARATED MYSELF\NFROM HIM HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:03.81.0:33:05.89.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE BEST I'VE EVER\NFUCKING BEEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:05.91.0:33:07.59.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S THE REASON WE DON'T GET\NALONG IS THIS HOUSE
Dialogue: 0.0:33:07.61.0:33:08.83.Default..0.0.0..IS BECAUSE OF HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:08.85.0:33:10.79.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T ARGUE WITH EVERYBODY\NIN THIS HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:10.82.0:33:12.73.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE-\NNOT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:12.75.0:33:14.73.Default..0.0.0..IT IS WHAT IT IS.\NAND THAT'S WHAT IT'S GONNA BE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:14.75.0:33:18.17.Default..0.0.0..OKAY.\NI'M GONNA GO OUTSIDE TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:18.19.0:33:21.37.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE NO PROBLEM. YOU KNOW.\NSTANDING BY MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:21.39.0:33:22.91.Default..0.0.0..NOT TOO MANY CAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:22.93.0:33:24.34.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. NONE OF 'EM\NIN THE HOUSE
Dialogue: 0.0:33:24.36.0:33:26.98.Default..0.0.0..CAN ACTUALLY STAND BY THEMSELVES\NEXCEPT ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.00.0:33:28.14.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHY THEY LIKE TO GANG UP\NAGAINST ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:28.17.0:33:29.61.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I'M JUST STRONG.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:29.64.0:33:34.72.Default..0.0.0..♪ NO MATTER HOW MUCH I WANT\NYOU TO STAY ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:33:34.74.0:33:40.32.Default..0.0.0..♪ IT'S A LIFE OF SOLITUDE\NTHAT I MUST PAY ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:33:40.35.0:33:45.25.Default..0.0.0..♪ THE PRICE OF AN ARTIST.\NTHE PRICE OF MY DREAMS ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:33:46.79.0:33:50.67.Default..0.0.0..VIN. HERE.\NCOME OVER HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:50.69.0:33:53.10.Default..0.0.0..I JUST THINK THAT. LIKE.\NLIVING WITH FUCKING MIKE
Dialogue: 0.0:33:53.13.0:33:55.84.Default..0.0.0..AND HAVING IT. LIKE. REMIND ME\NOF LAST YEAR'S BULLSHIT
Dialogue: 0.0:33:55.86.0:33:57.27.Default..0.0.0..IS FREAKING ME OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:57.30.0:33:58.91.Default..0.0.0..I MYSELF HAVE.\NLIKE. MY OWN...
Dialogue: 0.0:33:58.93.0:34:00.28.Default..0.0.0..YOUR OWN ISSUES.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:00.30.0:34:03.65.Default..0.0.0..SO I THINK HE'S GONNA EITHER\NHAVE TO CHANGE OR LEAVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:03.67.0:34:04.85.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:04.87.0:34:06.05.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK\NABOUT HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:06.07.0:34:07.62.Default..0.0.0..I'VE HAD ENOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:07.64.0:34:09.99.Default..0.0.0..HE'S GONNA CHANGE OR LEAVE.\NI'M DEAD SERIOUS AT THIS POINT.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:10.01.0:34:13.16.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. SORRY.\NHE IS GONNA CHANGE OR LEAVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:13.18.0:34:17.33.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE YOU CAN SEE IT.\NALL RIGHT. HERE IT COMES.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:17.35.0:34:19.23.Default..0.0.0..VINNY LOOKS LIKE\NHE'S ABOUT TO DO SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:19.25.0:34:22.17.Default..0.0.0..WHOEVER MIKE'S BEEN\NFUCKING WITH HAS TO TO TELL HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:22.19.0:34:24.77.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. "YO. YOU CAN'T DO THIS\NANYMORE."
Dialogue: 0.0:34:24.79.0:34:28.27.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE A... IT'S JUST\NLIKE A LOST CAUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:28.29.0:34:30.37.Default..0.0.0..IT'S EITHER LEAVE OR CHANGE.\NYOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:30.40.0:34:34.18.Default..0.0.0..BUT HE'S NOT GOING TO.\N'CAUSE HE CAN'T. HE CAN'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:34.20.0:34:35.65.Default..0.0.0..HE'S INCAPABLE.\NHE GETS IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:35.67.0:34:37.85.Default..0.0.0..EVERYONE FUCKING DOESN'T LIKE\NHIM. YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.87.0:34:39.12.Default..0.0.0..HE GETS THE POINT.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:39.14.0:34:40.65.Default..0.0.0..THE ONLY REASON\NHE'S ACTING LIKE THIS
Dialogue: 0.0:34:40.67.0:34:42.42.Default..0.0.0..IS OUT OF WHATEVER IT IS\NTHAT MAKES HIM HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:42.44.0:34:44.42.Default..0.0.0..MBB'S DEAD. LIKE. I MEAN.\NHE'S AROUND US.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:44.44.0:34:47.36.Default..0.0.0..HE'S AROUND US. WE ACQUAINTANCE\NOURSELF WITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:47.38.0:34:49.63.Default..0.0.0..BUT TO BE HONEST WITH YOU.\NIT'S VP.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:49.65.0:34:51.73.Default..0.0.0..MINE AND VINNY'S RELATIONSHIP\NIS BEAUTIFUL.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:51.75.0:34:53.70.Default..0.0.0..LIGHTS!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:53.72.0:34:55.43.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE HELL?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:55.46.0:34:56.73.Default..0.0.0..ONCE YOU GO TO SLEEP.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:56.76.0:34:57.80.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW\NWHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:57.82.0:34:59.30.Default..0.0.0..MY MAN VINNY LOVES ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:59.33.0:35:01.97.Default..0.0.0..WE HAVE A BROMANCE\NAND WE GET IT IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:05.83.0:35:07.31.Default..0.0.0..CAN I WATCH?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:10.30.0:35:14.28.Default..0.0.0..OH. WOW. YOU'RE THE ONE?\NI ALWAYS FIGURED.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:14.31.0:35:16.05.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. I'M TRYING TO DO SEX\NWITH PAULY.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:16.08.0:35:18.29.Default..0.0.0..HOW IS IT NOT GONNA RUIN\NTHEIR FRIENDSHIP?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:18.31.0:35:23.33.Default..0.0.0..WAIT. WAIT. WAIT. WAIT.\NI WAS GOING TO MY BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:23.35.0:35:25.49.Default..0.0.0..I FELL AND TRIPPED\NAND I ENDED UP...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.52.0:35:26.60.Default..0.0.0..AND THIS OPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:26.62.0:35:27.93.Default..0.0.0..SHH. DON'T TELL ANYBODY.\NRIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:27.95.0:35:29.27.Default..0.0.0..I'LL KILL YOU IF YOU TELL\NANYBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:29.29.0:35:30.67.Default..0.0.0..I SAW THE WHOLE THING.\NWAS IT HOT?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:30.69.0:35:32.90.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS REALLY GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:32.93.0:35:34.97.Default..0.0.0..OH. COME ON.\NDO IT AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:35.00.0:35:36.31.Default..0.0.0..YOU MISSED IT.\NIT'S OVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:36.33.0:35:39.36.Default..0.0.0..NO. DUDE. WHY WOULD YOU\NDO THAT WITHOUT ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:44.14.0:35:45.61.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:35:48.38.0:35:52.19.Default..0.0.0..CAN I USE THE BATHROOM?\NYEAH. WAIT ONE SECOND. GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:52.21.0:35:53.71.Default..0.0.0..THANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:00.85.0:36:02.06.Default..0.0.0..HELLO!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:03.26.0:36:04.83.Default..0.0.0..I'M LOCKED IN THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:04.86.0:36:09.64.Default..0.0.0..I'M LOCKED\NIN THE FUCKING BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:09.66.0:36:12.51.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:12.53.0:36:14.88.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. I HAVE TOLD MIKE NOT\NTO USE MY BATHROOM BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:14.90.0:36:16.71.Default..0.0.0..AND IT'S KIND OF LIKE\NKARMA'S A BITCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:16.74.0:36:21.05.Default..0.0.0..WHICH WAY DO YOU TURN IT IN?\NUP... FACING UP OR... OR DOWN?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:21.07.0:36:24.32.Default..0.0.0..HEY. DID I DO IT?\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:24.34.0:36:26.56.Default..0.0.0..WELL. DOES SOMEBODY\NWANT TO HELP ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:26.58.0:36:27.96.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I'M LOCKED IN HERE
Dialogue: 0.0:36:27.98.0:36:32.46.Default..0.0.0..AND I REALLY DON'T WANT TO\NKICK IT DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:32.49.0:36:34.42.Default..0.0.0..I WILL KICK IT DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:35.96.0:36:37.47.Default..0.0.0..HELLO!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:37.49.0:36:40.20.Default..0.0.0..I'M LOCKED IN THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:40.23.0:36:43.64.Default..0.0.0..RON? MIKE'S STUCK\NIN THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:43.66.0:36:46.44.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?\NCAN YOU HELP HIM OUT?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:46.47.0:36:48.48.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NWHAT BATHROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:48.50.0:36:50.81.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW. IT'S LIKE.\NWELL. FUCKING LEAVE HIM THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:50.84.0:36:52.22.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:52.24.0:36:53.25.Default..0.0.0..HE WANTS TO ACT LIKE SHIT.\NHE CAN LIVE IN THE TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:53.27.0:36:55.85.Default..0.0.0..HELLO!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:55.88.0:36:57.25.Default..0.0.0..IT'S OPEN.\NIT IS LOCKED?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:57.28.0:36:59.22.Default..0.0.0..YO. I-I DON'T WANT TO\NKICK IT DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:59.25.0:37:01.49.Default..0.0.0..TURN THE KEY.\NTURN THE KEY TO THE RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:01.51.0:37:02.79.Default..0.0.0..TO THE RIGHT?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.82.0:37:06.36.Default..0.0.0..I DID.\NI THINK IT'S JUST BROKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.39.0:37:09.30.Default..0.0.0..SHIT.\NTURN THE KEY RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:09.32.0:37:11.10.Default..0.0.0..SO MAYBE IT'S NOT THE KEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:12.23.0:37:13.54.Default..0.0.0..NO. I DID ALREADY.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:13.56.0:37:15.54.Default..0.0.0..OH. GOD. OH. GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:15.56.0:37:17.41.Default..0.0.0..I WAS GONNA KICK IT. BUT I\NDIDN'T WANT TO BE MEAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:17.43.0:37:19.21.Default..0.0.0..I'D RATHER YOU BREAK IT\NTHAN ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:19.23.0:37:20.94.Default..0.0.0..THEY GET MAD AT ME\NIN THIS HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:20.97.0:37:22.85.Default..0.0.0..I THINK MIKE WAS GONNA\NDO THE CRANE KICK
Dialogue: 0.0:37:22.87.0:37:24.28.Default..0.0.0..TO TRY TO GET HIMSELF\NOUT OF THE DOOR.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.30.0:37:26.08.Default..0.0.0..BUT I DON'T THINK HE WANTED\NTO BREAK THE DOOR.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:26.11.0:37:27.62.Default..0.0.0..SO HE ACTUALLY USED HIS HEAD\NFOR ONCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:27.64.0:37:29.35.Default..0.0.0..WELL. NOT LIKE HE DID\NON THE WALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:29.38.0:37:31.22.Default..0.0.0..BUT HE USED HIS HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:31.24.0:37:33.85.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T BELIEVE I JUST GOT\NLOCKED IN THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:38.59.0:37:41.36.Default..0.0.0..YO. I GOT THE FRESHEST BLOWOUT\NIN FIRENZE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:41.39.0:37:43.90.Default..0.0.0..I THINK YOU HAVE THE ONLY\NBLOWOUT IN FIRENZE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:43.92.0:37:45.17.Default..0.0.0..EITHER WAY.\NWHO'S HATING?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:45.19.0:37:47.47.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK MAD GUIDETTE.\NESPECIALLY FROM THE BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:47.49.0:37:49.64.Default..0.0.0..I LIKE LOOKING GUIDETTE.\NDUH!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:49.66.0:37:53.04.Default..0.0.0..WELL. GET SOME REST. GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:53.07.0:37:54.94.Default..0.0.0..YO. WE'RE READY TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:56.20.0:37:57.48.Default..0.0.0..IT'S RIGHT HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:57.50.0:37:59.08.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU DIDN'T KNOW ME.\NWOULD YOU FUCK ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:59.11.0:38:00.25.Default..0.0.0..HELL YEAH.\NCOOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:03.28.0:38:11.22.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:38:15.56.0:38:18.17.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. EVERY NIGHT\NIN ITALY AND JERSEY
Dialogue: 0.0:38:18.19.0:38:20.37.Default..0.0.0..SHOULD FEEL THE WAY IT FEELS\NTONIGHT:
Dialogue: 0.0:38:20.39.0:38:23.17.Default..0.0.0..HAVING A GOOD TIME\NWITHOUT DRAMA.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:23.20.0:38:27.01.Default..0.0.0..GO. RONNIE! GO. RONNIE! GO!\NGO. RONNIE! GO. RONNIE! GO!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:27.03.0:38:31.51.Default..0.0.0..GO. RONNIE. GO!\NGO. GO. GO!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:31.54.0:38:33.35.Default..0.0.0..EVERYBODY'S HAVING FUN\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:33.37.0:38:34.98.Default..0.0.0..AND I KIND OF FELT ALONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:38.75.0:38:41.26.Default..0.0.0..I WENT TO THE BAR TO GET\NONE LAST DRINK.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:41.28.0:38:43.63.Default..0.0.0..AND SOME GUY LOOKED AT ME\NTHE WRONG WAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:43.65.0:38:44.86.Default..0.0.0..HEY. HEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:44.89.0:38:46.30.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T WANT TO FUCK\NWITH ME. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:46.32.0:38:48.13.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T WANT TO DO IT.\NYOU DON'T WANT TO DO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:48.15.0:38:49.63.Default..0.0.0..HE'S A HATER!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:49.66.0:38:50.93.Default..0.0.0..{...}.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:50.96.0:38:52.60.Default..0.0.0..DON'T LISTEN TO HIM!\NDON'T LISTEN TO HIM!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:52.63.0:38:53.80.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M LIKE.\NFUCK THIS SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:53.83.0:38:55.27.Default..0.0.0..I'M. PSSHH. LIKE. READY TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:55.30.0:38:56.54.Default..0.0.0..LET'S DO THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:56.56.0:38:57.81.Default..0.0.0..HEY. BRO. BRO. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:57.83.0:38:59.51.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A PUSSY.\NYOU'RE A PUSSY.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:59.53.0:39:02.48.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FUCK YOU UP.\NI'LL FUCK YOU UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:05.01.0:39:06.38.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. LIKE.\NWHEN HE GETS IN A CLUB.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:06.41.0:39:08.88.Default..0.0.0..HE KNOWS HE HAS US.\NSO HE STARTS TALKING SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:08.91.0:39:09.89.Default..0.0.0..AND THINKS HE'S TOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:09.91.0:39:11.05.Default..0.0.0..FUCKING BITCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:11.08.0:39:12.59.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A BITCH.\NMOTHERFUCKER!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:12.61.0:39:14.26.Default..0.0.0..IF MIKE RIGHT NOW\NGETS INTO A FIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.28.0:39:15.49.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA JUMP IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:15.52.0:39:17.69.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GO.\NTHE FUCK OUT OF HERE!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.72.0:39:19.46.Default..0.0.0..I'LL EAT YOU.\NMOTHERFUCKER!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:19.49.0:39:21.33.Default..0.0.0..WHO'S GOT YOUR BACK\NWHEN YOU'RE FIGHTING?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:21.35.0:39:23.20.Default..0.0.0..WHEN YOU TURN AROUND AND LOOK\NWHO'S WITH YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:23.22.0:39:31.22.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHO YOUR FRIENDS ARE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:37.60.0:39:38.64.Default..0.0.0..AND IT'S JUST ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:42.98.0:39:45.56.Default..0.0.0..♪ I USED TO BE A SOLDIER ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:39:45.58.0:39:47.66.Default..0.0.0..♪ BUT THEY TOOK MY SOUL ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:39:47.68.0:39:50.03.Default..0.0.0..♪ WHOO ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:39:50.05.0:39:52.56.Default..0.0.0..♪ NOW I AM SOBER ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:39:52.59.0:39:53.96.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'VE GOT ALL MY CONTROL ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:39:53.99.0:39:55.70.Default..0.0.0..THE SITUATION'S\NIN THE CRIB.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:55.72.0:39:57.70.Default..0.0.0..I'M ABOUT TO BEAT SOMEBODY\NTHE FUCK UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:57.72.0:39:59.90.Default..0.0.0..♪ I SUFFER. SUFFER.\NSUFFER. SUFFER. SUFFER ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:39:59.93.0:40:02.00.Default..0.0.0..♪ GOD WON'T GIVE ME A BREAK ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:02.03.0:40:04.61.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:07.63.0:40:13.57.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:18.38.0:40:20.56.Default..0.0.0..♪ I USED TO BE A FIGHTER ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:20.58.0:40:25.90.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:25.92.0:40:28.75.Default..0.0.0..CHEERS TO A GOOD NIGHT.\NBITCHES.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:33.16.0:40:36.04.Default..0.0.0..I'M ALWAYS THE BAD GUY.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:36.06.0:40:39.34.Default..0.0.0..I CAN ONLY IMAGINE\NWHEN THERE'S NO BAD GUY.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:39.37.0:40:41.74.Default..0.0.0..WHO'S GONNA BE THE BAD GUY?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:41.77.0:40:45.44.Default..0.0.0..THE SITUATION?\NNO PROBLEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:59.79.0:41:02.72.Default..0.0.0..Captioning by{\c&H00ff00&} CaptionMax{\c}\Nwww.captionmax.com
